codas: a data display system.wcodas, a customer oriented data system, isa user-oriented data retrieval and display system.  the command language of the system provides the userwith an easy means for specifying data retrieval and display requests.  data is displayed as tables andgraphs produced in a format ready for publication.  in this paper the statements of the request languageand the general system design are described.cacm february, day, r. h.mansfield, m. k.ellis, m. e..kdata display, information retrieval, graphic display,command languages, report program generation, management data processing.c. . . . . . . .ca jb february ,   : am